    <li><a href="/docs/configuration">Configuration</a> — every setting, in detail.</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/ocr">OCR &amp; text extraction</a> — how to grab the <code>.txt</code> of any screenshot.</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/mcp">MCP integration</a> — plug SnapLink into Claude Desktop.</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/faq">FAQ</a> — quick answers to the questions we get most.</li>
  </ul>
